These methods do work , but only the minority of the population is doing it , and results can only be seen after many years of efforts .
Instead of reducing the carbon emission , we can solve this impending crisis by finding some methods that reduce the heat source or are able to manipulate the heat input on Earth .
Research has shown that whenever a volcano erupts , it releases a large amount of and gaseous chemicals causing a thick layer of haze to form around the planet , thus reducing the average temperature of Earth by almost one degree Fahrenheit .
