The examination-oriented education , as the name implies , is an education system whose purpose is for students to get high grades in the exam .
Teachers teach to the exam .
This results in students getting high scores but having low abilities .
In the third step of the design process , generating multiple solutions , divergent thinking and analytical are needed , whereas the examinationoriented education does not emphasis the importance of thinking and skills .
Its only purpose is high scores in the exam .
The skills which are needed in the design process can not be gained from such an education system .
China has already found ways to solve these problems , but solving these problems needs time .
