Immigrants who have the skills and expertise in the various industries are favoured by employers .
This is because they can contribute their knowledge and bring the companies to greater heights .
Hence , this has caused Singaporeans who are not as proficient to become unemployed .
The introduction of working-age immigrants has also increased the competition in the workforce .
With the influx of immigrants and foreign talents , most Singaporeans believe that Singapore 's current population is considerably large .
