However , because of overeating high protein food , lack of exercise and many other relevant reasons , various kinds of disease are threatening us human beings , especially the heart disease .
Till now , heart attack has become the top one killer among all the diseases which threaten the human 's health .
According to a research conducted in 2000 , the number of people dying from heart attack accounts for almost one-third of the total number of deaths around the world , and even worse the percentage is expected to be greatly enhanced by 2020 .
As a result , WHO says heart attack is the 21st century 's plague and calls for more attention on the heart disease .
Fortunately , the appearance of a kind of engineering design product helps huge numbers of patients who suffer a lot from heart attack .
That is the heart pacemaker .
With the help of a pacemaker , patients whose heart rate is too high or too low can maintain an adequate heart rate .
Because the heart pacemaker should be implanted into the patient 's body before it can work well , it calls for higher safety requirement .
The material used to make a pacemaker is silicon , titanium steel and special artificial plastic , both of them are quite friendly to the patients ' internal environment and will not cause injury or other diseases to humans .
An engineer should seriously consider that the pacemaker is used to save the patient 's life . If it suddenly breaks down , the patient will face the risk of losing his life .
Originally , the battery of the heart pacemaker was made up of mercury-zinc which at most can only work for 2-3years .
Such short lifespan of the battery together with some other reasons lead to a few cases of patients ' death because of the battery running out of energy in advance .
Nowadays , the engineers adopt the lithium cell which has a great advantage over the older one for it can last for 10 years and is much lighter .
The success of applying the lithium battery into the heart pacemaker brings a substantial increase in reliability .
Since the main purpose of the heart pacemaker is to save people who have heart disease , the price can not be too high to afford .
Reasonable price promotes the wider use of the heart pacemaker around the world .
Overall , the invention of the heart pacemaker makes a tremendous contribution to the patients who suffer from heart attack .
Let us hope the prospective heart pacemaker can be more convenient and have more powerful features at lower price .
