The population of Singapore will increase from the current 4.8 million people to 6.5 million people in the coming years
It will cost more and it will be hard for the organization in order to be in Singapore to proceed with the engineering innovation process .
Infrastructure will also be a problem for the organization due to lack of land area .
Organizations in other countries too meet many significant difficulties during their innovation designing process .
