Despite his old age , he still contributes to society by making major decisions for the country .
This shows that an elderly person is never a useless person in the society .
On the contrary , they are the ones who can make the wisest decisions .
In addition to the above mentioned factors , the elderly have already contributed many years of their youth to society .
If not for them , Singapore would never have become a developed country .
