To solve this problem , people have tried to find different energy substitutions , among which is nuclear energy .
As carbon dioxide emission soars and energy demands have increased rapidly in years , the nuclear option is finding its way to the table .
Consequently , generation IV nuclear systems were born , which includes six models .
Generation IV International Forum ( GIF ) , as the authority in nuclear power development , has shown data which demonstrates that the basic technology for the VHTR has been well established in former High Temperature Gas Reactors plants .
