However , the two accidents were both due to human factors rather than the reactors ' own deflects .
What 's more , many scientists have studied the operation security of VHTR , like He on the Third International Topical Meeting on High Temperature Reactor Technology in South Africa and put forward some constructive suggestions to improve the security condition of high temperature reactors .
Considering all these , we should have confidence that we will build secure nuclear reactors which will avoid tragedies
