When high cost eventually returns us the ample energy supply and clean and comfortable living environment , all the seeming expensive cost is worth spending .
Moreover , the oil and coal crisis forces us to search for substitutions , or else , we could not survive in future competitions .
It deserves all the effort , in terms of security insurance and work efficiency .
So now we should pay more attention to the developing progress and give more financial support .
