Moreover , compared to the increasingly expensive fossil fuels , it is reasonable to use nuclear energy .
Nevertheless , according to Idaho National Laboratory 's study ( 2009 ) , the VHTR system should be highly-efficient .
During different processes , the heat can be re-circulated .
To make the system perform better , electricity generating equipment may be added in .
Therefore , the VHTR provides a number of processes to use the heat and produce electricity efficiently .
