Last but not least , people may be concerned about the efficiency of robotic surgery .
There are doubts as to whether the surgeons will be able to perform robotic surgeries effectively .
This concern is reasonable because if the surgeon is not familiar with the system , he may take longer time for the surgery , thus creating a risk .
Professional engineers and foreign experts are invited to train the local surgeons with certain hours of practicing to ensure the surgeons are fully familiar with the system and will be able to perform in real situations .
This is beneficial especially in the case of Singapore as there are limited skilled assistants available in hospital .
Also , with the help of robots , the fatigue of the surgeon will be reduced as most work is done by robots and time taken for each surgery is generally shortened .
