Under the concept of SCWR , Butler ( 2004 ) also states that SCWRs have simple safety features that do not depend on well-trained operators and complex backup systems .
Opponents of nuclear energy might argue that the radioactive waste which will be produced by nuclear reactors is susceptible to accidents due to human intervention .
However , researchers could only suggest better solutions for nuclear plants to produce less radioactive waste but not to the extent of eliminating radioactive waste till today .
